Case 02 - Billing Invoice Error
Date: 24 Dec 2025
Platform/Tool: Example SaaS App
Category: Billing / Subscription Support

Short Description:
Customer reported an incorrect invoice total. 
Demonstrates troubleshooting billing errors, recalculating invoices,
and communicating solutions to maintain trust.

Extended Description:
This case highlights resolving billing-related issues in SaaS platforms. 
The customer received an invoice that was higher than expected due to a system miscalculation. 
The case emphasizes technical knowledge of subscription systems, attention to detail, 
and professional communication to ensure customer satisfaction while preventing recurring errors.

Issue Summary:
Customer noticed that the latest invoice reflected an incorrect total, raising concerns about potential double charges.

Steps Taken:
Verified the customerâ€™s subscription plan, billing history, and invoice details.
Identified a system error where a prorated discount was not applied correctly.
Recalculated the correct amount using internal finance dashboards.
Issued the corrected invoice via email.
Explained the error and measures to prevent future occurrences.
Followed up to confirm customer satisfaction.
Outcome / Resolution:
Customer received the corrected invoice, confirmed accuracy, and expressed appreciation for the quick and professional handling of the issue.
Skills Demonstrated:
Troubleshooting SaaS billing and invoicing errors
Attention to detail in financial workflows
Clear, professional communication
Using internal dashboards for verification and correction
Ensuring customer satisfaction through follow-up
